{"tid":1208882,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"而家同班警硬碰 冇著數","createTime":"2019-06-12T10:26:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T10:36:45.000Z","uid":197216,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a5f52ebba6f34eb2e5791d974e87e478e30b02c3","tid":1208882,"uid":197216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T10:26:21.000Z","msg":"班警明顯地失去理智<br />\n見人就打 見人就射<br />\n好明顯 係唔打死你都打殘你<br />\n最好打斷你手腳 射到你永久失明<br />\n<br />\n前線呢班警根本就係 冇文化冇思考能力既一班人<br />\n<br />\n我相信佢地每一棍 每一次開槍<br />\n都係純粹發洩 <br />\n<br />\n手無寸鐵既示威者只會係落敗既一方<br />\n<br />\n我既建議係 金鐘已經冇得搞落去<br />\n<br />\n轉場過尖咀 尖咀搞唔到落去 再轉場<br />\n<br />\n而家唔係單單反修例 根本係成個香港政府都係有問題<br />\n<br />\n長期玩野 比起一鋪過end game 應該更有效"},{"pid":"3e87f089f475839835cb7b33b372cac27b53f83f","tid":1208882,"uid":152048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T10:26:54.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"45a12ca887137b272954d1c34b6816bb8dd84c3c","tid":1208882,"uid":197216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T10:29:41.000Z","msg":"示威者 如果因為咁樣 永久傷殘<br />\n一d都唔值得 倒不如不停轉場<br />\n要班警 疲於奔命 冇得休息<br />\nOn call 一個月"},{"pid":"58ccfb0514556d443beee3a5237baf4ff1b038ff","tid":1208882,"uid":197216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e87f089f475839835cb7b33b372cac27b53f83f","tid":1208882,"uid":152048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T10:26:54.000Z","msg":"push"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T10:31:26.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2da828ba2a9e9af1abfad237d00e9215f30dd17b","tid":1208882,"uid":197216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58ccfb0514556d443beee3a5237baf4ff1b038ff","tid":1208882,"uid":197216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e87f089f475839835cb7b33b372cac27b53f83f","tid":1208882,"uid":152048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T10:26:54.000Z","msg":"push"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T10:31:26.000Z","msg":"Push"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T10:34:23.000Z","msg":"Pu